TH_YOUMU-UNEXHAUSTED_SOUL.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage; reduce this card's damage by the number of cards in your [gold]Exhaust Pile[/gold].
If the damage dealt is not less than this card's base value, choose a card from your [gold]Exhaust Pile[/gold] and return it to your hand.{InCombat:
 (Damage reduced by {ExhaustReduction:diff()})|}

TH_YOUMU-BEYOND_SWORD.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage to random enemies {Cards:diff()} times.
Increase this card's damage by 1 for each [purple]Curse[/purple] or [red]Status[/red] card you have (wherever they are).{InCombat:
 (Deal {BonusDamage:diff()} extra damage)|}
